    "118843692": {
      "title": "On a martingale method for symmetric diffusion proces and its applications",
      "abstract": "Let X be a locally compact separable metric space and in be a Radon measure on X whose support is the whole space X. A symetric Markov process associated with a Dirichlet space on L 2 (X,m) is considered. Using a formula of Lyons-Zheng for an additive functional this process is studied by means of the martingale theory. A conservativeness criterion, a tightness criterion and some sample path properties for symmetric diffusion processes are found, with extensions of the method to non-symmetric situations"
    }
